<p>Collection and category pages are undervalued in ecommerce SEO. Most stores optimize individual products and ignore the broader category terms that represent earlier stages of the buying journey. A well-optimized collection page for "women's pajamas" can drive more traffic than 50 individual product pages because it captures the broader search intent.</p>
